   <h2> [转帖]JOJO奇妙冒险&amp;星际online=俘虏 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=3773&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=469&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2> 
   <div class="plc cl" id="pid53837"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://www.jojo-china.com/gp/uc_server/avatar.php?uid=469&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
